<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wiguläus Schenk von Geyern, Amtmann zu Burgthann</head><p>Der Rat bittet für H. Müllner, Armmann zu Unterferrieden der Ehefrau des Fritz Muffel, Bürgerin zu Nürnberg, um Freilassung und um Austrag vor dem Burggrafen von Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_111" id="54r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_111_r1l21">VVigleis <expan>Schenck<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Geÿ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_111_r1l22">Amptman cʒu <expan>Tan<ex>n</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_111_r1l23">Lieber vvigleis / Als wir euch voꝛmals auch <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haben / von <expan cert="unknown">h</expan> <expan>Mülln<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_111_r1l24">von Nıdernberrıden der fritʒen Müfflin vnſer Burgerin <expan>Arme<ex>n</ex>mans</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_111_r1l25">vvegen / etc Alſo hat vns derſelbe <expan cert="unknown">H</expan> <expan>Mülln<ex>er</ex></expan> aber fürbracht vvie Jr Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_111_r1l26"><expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> vencknüſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_111_r1l27">noch nicht ledig gelaſʒen habt / vnd vvie er ſich <expan>ÿetʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> ſtellen muſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_111_r1l28"><expan>Rogam<ex>us</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr durch vnſern willen demſelben <expan>vnſer<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>Burgerin</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_111_r1l29">~ <expan>arme<ex>n</ex>man</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> noch </del> lenger tag geben wöllet / ob wir das gen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_111_r1l30"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem <expan>~Burg<ex>ra</ex>fen</expan> auſʒgetragen möchten Als etc das <expan>woll<ex>en</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_111_r1l32"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die <expan>S<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Michahelis <expan>Arch<ex>angeli</ex></expan> Anno etc Octauo / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_111" id="54r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wigleis <expan>Schenck<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                        <expan>Gey<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, amptman czu <expan>Tan<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber Wigleis als wir euch vormals auch <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
                        haben von <expan cert="unknown">H.</expan>
<expan>Mülln<ex>er</ex>s</expan> von Nidernberriden, der Friczen Müfflin,
                        unser burgerin, <expan>arme<ex>n</ex>mans</expan> wegen etc. Also hat uns
                        derselbe <expan cert="unknown">H.</expan>
<expan>Mülln<ex>er</ex></expan> aber fürbracht, wie ir in
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> vencknüsz noch nicht ledig gelaszen habt
                        und wie er sich <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> stellen musz.
                                <expan>Rogam<ex>us</ex></expan>, daz ir durch unsern willen
                        demselben <expan>unser<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>burgerin</expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex>man</expan> lenger tag geben wöllet, ob wir das gen
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem <expan>burg<ex>ra</ex>fen</expan>,
                        auszgetragen möchten, als etc. Das <expan>woll<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                            <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Michahelis
                                <expan>arch<ex>angeli</ex></expan> anno etc. octavo.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
